text: Alan Villafuerte (born 29 June 1977) is a Dutch trampoline gymnast. He represented the Netherlands at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney, Australia and at the 2004 Summer Olympics in Athens, Greece. In the men's trampoline competition in 2000 he finished in 7th place.
